<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #0a173b;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header img {
        max-width: 150px;
        height: auto;
      }
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin: 10px 0 0 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    "
  >
    <!-- Header -->
    <div
      class="header"
      style="
        background-color: #0a173b;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 5px;
      "
    >
      <img
        src="https://va-claims-assets.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/VA_Claims_Main_Logo_Transparent_2_200px.png"
        alt="VA Claims Academy Logo"
        style="max-width: 100px; height: auto"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Email Body -->
    <div style="padding: 20px">
      <p style="font-size: 16px">Hi <%= name %>,</p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        Great news! Your VetVictory Claim Guide is now ready for your review.
        This is an exciting step forward in your journey!
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        <strong style="color: #0a173b"
          >Your VetVictory Claim Guide is packed with valuable insights about
          your claim and our expert recommendations for moving forward.</strong
        >
        It's a crucial tool in strengthening your case for the benefits you've
        earned.
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        We encourage you to review it carefully. Every detail in this blueprint
        brings you closer to mastering your claim and securing the benefits you
        deserve.
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        Ready to dive in? Just click the button below to access your
        personalized VetVictory Claim Guide:
      </p>

      <p style="text-align: center">
        <a
          href="<%= reportLink %>"
          style="
            background-color: #0a173b;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
          "
          >View Your VetVictory Claim Guide</a
        >
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        If you have any questions about your VetVictory Claim Guide or would
        like to discuss its contents, don't hesitate to reach out. We're here to
        support you every step of the way.
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        Keep pushing forward â€“ you're making great progress!
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div
      style="
        margin-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
        padding-top: 10px;
        font-size: 16px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
      "
    >
      <p style="font-size: 16px">
        In your corner,<br />
        VA Claims Academy Team
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
